{"tid":1168751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國瑜又草包!稱「瑞士非聯合國」人渣文本：應該先孤狗","createTime":"2019-05-24T01:52:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T02:32:15.000Z","uid":35790,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c54bde4225538b76a7f329b677ee871119a244fc","tid":1168751,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T01:52:02.000Z","msg":"韓國瑜又草包!稱「瑞士非聯合國」人渣文本：應該先孤狗<br />\n<br />\n高雄市長韓國瑜昨（23）日受媒體專訪時，大談中美貿易戰中台灣的角色定位，其中，他指出許多人都覺得台灣不是聯合國會員國是最劣的劣勢，但他反而認為是優勢，因為「歐洲瑞士」也不是聯合國會員國。不過此番言論反遭網友砲轟，指出瑞士早於2002年就加入聯合國！<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜受《聯合新聞網》專訪時認為，台灣不是聯合國會員國，反而是求之不得的優勢，在某部分有無窮無盡的空間去發展，可以學瑞士做永久中立國；但此言論卻被網友罵翻，因為早在2002年，瑞士就舉行公投決定申請加入聯合國，最後也於同年入聯，就算在2002年前，瑞士於1948年至2002年間也是聯合國的常任觀察員國。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/05/24/1939550-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F05%2F24%2F1939550-XXL.jpg&h=621b445a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲聯合國早於2002年就已加入聯合國。（圖／翻攝自維基百科）<br />\n<br />\n對此，筆名「人渣文本」的輔大助理教授周偉航就指出，瑞士明明就是聯合國會員國，同時也奉勸韓國瑜「講大話前應該先孤狗一下，一分鐘就可以堵起大腦的洞」。<br />\n<br />\n許多網友則紛紛表示「草包一開口，就知什麼都沒有」、「不要這樣逼他，他有講對瑞士而非瑞典就已經很對得起89萬2545票了唷！」、「瑞士：呵呵～你是不是以為我是不丹」、「&hellip;&hellip;這種人總統民調最高，足以顯示民智低弱到什麼程度」、「」、「政大東亞所的入學資格是拿雞腿換的嗎？」<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=545733\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D545733&d=jM2msIR27xdcbllsFNIWhLc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=8f9451a6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D545733&h=7f78a17c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=545733</a>"},{"pid":"de849b60737aa05ad85a7776a2b4c8a771367663","tid":1168751,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T01:55:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d5fa6f06b349baeb5d9d3e621893d447c6a7865","tid":1168751,"uid":25794,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T01:56:57.000Z","msg":"發大財"},{"pid":"a27a548ad964e37ae9cc0311d327dfe56c69a13e","tid":1168751,"uid":116027,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T01:57:53.000Z","msg":"聯合國早於2002年就已加入聯合國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47f7c92f3942b62420de770e2912943b94ef4c68","tid":1168751,"uid":16343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T01:59:01.000Z","msg":"台灣班弱智選埋佢做總統啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"004b288c9b7943f32fa8daf6a687f0c3d890c9d4","tid":1168751,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47f7c92f3942b62420de770e2912943b94ef4c68","tid":1168751,"uid":16343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T01:59:01.000Z","msg":"台灣班弱智選埋佢做總統啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T01:59:50.000Z","msg":"G持韓國瑜代表國民黨參選總統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d8f97f1ad6b986de69116a40880d733abc696e7","tid":1168751,"uid":68132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T02:03:02.000Z","msg":"最緊要發大財"},{"pid":"80eba58bb04b8bca59b543a9f253d056786d2e3b","tid":1168751,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T02:04:39.000Z","msg":"@黃毓民"},{"pid":"b86665c0be040694f44f3b2ad4acc6c92dc188bb","tid":1168751,"uid":134215,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a27a548ad964e37ae9cc0311d327dfe56c69a13e","tid":1168751,"uid":116027,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T01:57:53.000Z","msg":"聯合國早於2002年就已加入聯合國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T02:15:08.000Z","msg":"亞太區有一天會成為亞太區 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56aab67e4cdcf5afe5dc96716a9eda501bd327b2","tid":1168751,"uid":79442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite